ithonline\/2019\/07\/12\/recite-quran-by-heart\/","url_meta":{"origin":12615,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Encouragement to memorize, not only read Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Qasim reported: Abu Umamah, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cRecite the Quran and do not be deceived by depending on the written copies. Verily, Allah will never punish a heart that has preserved the Quran.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 34044 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14474,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/31\/abu-umamah-salaam-non-muslims\/","url_meta":{"origin":12615,"position":5},"title":"Abu Umamah on Salaam: Initiating greetings of peace to non-Musims","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 31, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Urwah ibn Ruwaym reported: I saw Abu Umamah al-Bahili, may Allah be pleased with him, greet with peace whomever he would meet among the Muslims and non-Muslim citizens. Abu Umamah would say, \u201cThis is the greeting for the people of our religion, an assurance of security for the people of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/12615","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuamina